inner_text: The simplest and fastest way to get up and running with Tailwind CSS from scratch is with the Tailwind CLI tool. The CLI is also available as a standalone executable if you want to use it without installing Node.js.

inner_text:

Install tailwindcss via npm, and create your tailwind.config.js file.
